latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Acne is one of the most common skin conditions
worldwide and can have a substantial impact on quality of
life, both physically and emotionally. June is dedicated to
‘Acne Awareness Month’ and we start off by sharing
Eungyu‘s Skinterview’, a story about the emotional impact
acne had on him when growing up and how he’s finally
reclaimed his confidence. Watch now. ❤

latestIgtvVideos.title: Anti-Pigment Routine
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Reducing pigment spots in two weeks! Please meet our Anti-Pigment Range with patented Thiamidol. Your daily routine could look like this @sophie_je_suis 🤗

1. Use cleansing products from the Eucerin DermatoClean range for an effective cleansing experience.

2. Apply Eucerin Anti-Pigment Dual Serum and/or
Eucerin Anti-Pigment Spot Corrector before your moisturizer.

3. Moisturize your skin with Eucerin Anti-Pigment Day SPF 30 in the morning and Eucerin Anti-Pigment Night in the evening.

#eucerin #antipigment #skincare
